-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529082\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 02, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jwi1667387512874.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jwi1667387512874.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jwi1667387512874.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jwi1667387512874\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The following section provides resolution for the error which occurs while registering\n\t\tyour Registration Token.</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__context_m4y_hps_jvb\">If an error occurs while registering your Registration\n\t\t\tToken, check whether:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__ul_dfc_4ps_jvb\">\n<li class=\"li\">You have entered the Registration Token correctly</li>\n<li class=\"li\">You have connection to the internet</li>\n<li class=\"li\">The Entitlement ID is activated on the Sentinel EMS Customer Portal</li>\n<li class=\"li\">You have exceeded the count of the Registration Token</li>\n<li class=\"li\">The number of sessions is greater than the quantity of licenses you have on your\n\t\t\t\t\tEntitlement (sessions are listed per license feature)</li>\n<li class=\"li\">The Registration Token is still valid</li>\n</ul><div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__note_ecw_xps_jvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Registration Tokens have an expiry set when they are\n\t\t\t\tcreated. They are valid for a maximum of 30 days. The Registration Token must be\n\t\t\t\tregistered within this period in order to connect to the Cloud License\n\t\t\t\tManager.</div><p class=\"p\">To troubleshoot further:</p></section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__step_w556ab1b5b3b1_w557ab1b5b3_w558ab1b5_w559ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Add the following to [SETTINGS] in your <span class=\"keyword wintitle\">ulic.asn</span>\n\t\t\t\t\tfile:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104jwi1667387512874_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__codeblock_qmy_cqs_jvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SETTINGS] \ntrace $trc_start=usyslog:&lt;trace file name&gt;.log \n$trc_levels=9L</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__step_w560ab1b5b3b3_w561ab1b5b3_w562ab1b5_w563ab1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Check the trace file for any error codes, for example:</span>\n<ul class=\"ul choices\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__choices_gkx_gqs_jvb\">\n<li class=\"li choice\">\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jwi1667387512874__ul_wkf_hqs_jvb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">210001SNTL_NO_LICENSE_GIVEN</code>—the licensing token for\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\ta given feature cannot be obtained, for example if the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tauthentication token has not yet been generated.</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">210018SNTL_NO_SUCH_FEATURE</code>—the requested feature is\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnot available on the Entitlement.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For a full list of error codes and a description of the error, see the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://docs.sentinel.thalesgroup.com/softwareandservices/RMS/RMSDocumentation/APIREF/Content/Unified_API_Error_Code.htm\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Licensing Library Error and Result\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCodes</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529082\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529082\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Troubleshooting Cloud LM Licensing Issues Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 02, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The following section provides resolution for the error which occurs while registering your Registration Token. If an error occurs while registering your Registration Token, check whether: You have entered the Registration Token correctly You have connection to the internet The Entitlement ID is activated on the Sentinel EMS Customer Portal You have exceeded the count of the Registration Token The number of sessions is greater than the quantity of licenses you have on your Entitlement (sessions are listed per license feature) The Registration Token is still valid Note: Registration Tokens have an expiry set when they are created. They are valid for a maximum of 30 days. The Registration Token must be registered within this period in order to connect to the Cloud License Manager. To troubleshoot further: Add the following to [SETTINGS] in your ulic.asn file: Explain this code [SETTINGS] trace $trc_start=usyslog:<trace file name>.log $trc_levels=9L Copy Check the trace file for any error codes, for example: 210001SNTL_NO_LICENSE_GIVEN —the licensing token for a given feature cannot be obtained, for example if the authentication token has not yet been generated. 210018SNTL_NO_SUCH_FEATURE —the requested feature is not available on the Entitlement. For a full list of error codes and a description of the error, see the Licensing Library Error and Result Codes . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}